          "quantityNote": "1/2 cup"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Greek Salad Bowl",
      "ingredientsText": "1 head Lettuce\n1 medium Cucumber\n2 medium Tomato\n150 g Feta Cheese\n1/2 cup Olive\n1 Lemon",
      "instructions": "1. Chop the lettuce, cucumber, and tomato into bite-sized pieces.\n2. Combine in a bowl with olives and crumbled feta.\n3. Squeeze lemon over the top and toss gently before serving.",
