    {
      "title": "Chicken and Broccoli Rice",
      "ingredientsText": "500 g Chicken\n1 head Broccoli\n3 tbsp Soy Sauce\n1 tbsp Ginger\n2 cloves Garlic\n1 cup White Rice",
